{"tid":1561953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次跳閘跳衰左 然後....","createTime":"2019-09-11T22:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T14:47:53.000Z","uid":312579,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4106e90c5d62250a0e43f864060762ac89e89705","tid":1561953,"uid":312579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:08:34.000Z","msg":"恕小妹生得矮 怕唔夠腳長跳閘<br />\n所以一直以黎只係試過捐閘 <br />\n但捐閘嘅時候 唔係捐落去嗰下撞到個頭 就係企起身嗰下撞到背蔗 拖慢晒成個流程<br />\n平時見啲手足輕輕鬆鬆跳閘 唔會撞到 效率又快<br />\n所以小妹今日趁人少少試下練習跳閘<br />\n唔好彩係落地個下失衡仆左個大街 仆到成身都係瘀痕同傷口<br />\n我抬頭望望右邊 有2個廢佬走向我 <br />\n佢憤怒嘅眼神話我知我瀨野了<br />\n我即刻爬番起身一仆一碌咁跑走 最後走得甩<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 我寧願仆大街 都唔會比錢搭黨鐵！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跳一次衰左 練多幾次一定會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之就核爆都唔會比錢黨鐵賺！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1a99ef4af06ae14100fc88b84a850f49cb6859","tid":1561953,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"891c9e5d4c6b50788e3b797d643f252a9d9ed5fd","tid":1561953,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:08:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h